  yearlyPrice = 280.00, 
  yearlyDiscount = 7,
  maxKeys = 2500,
  maxFolders = 1500,
  maxGeneratedKeys = -1
WHERE name = 'Corporate';

UPDATE plans SET 
  maxGeneratedKeys = 10
WHERE name = 'Free';
